value: It seems､ in the end､ we stayed until the close of the party… Thank you for your accompaniment.
Aah… The matcha and yokan are delicious. To think､ there could be a traditional sweets café in a place like this as well.
Phew… we finally have a chance to take a break. It seems there were too many things I was unfamiliar with.
Thank you very much. I really am quite exhausted､ but… I did gain something from it.
Among those whom I had the chance to talk with､ there were also people who knew of Sai､
And I managed to converse with many of the youths about tea ceremonies.
It was a truly valuable experience､ being able to talk with those whom I would otherwise have few contact points with.
Fufu､ I must give my thanks to the one who invited me to the party､ it seems.
…Regardless､ talking with you in a place like this does calm me down､ Producer.
It’s as I thought; I suit serene spaces more､ much like that of this traditional café.
